{
  "stem": "2539.2",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, it was very soon after we had to leave Olyka, and-- because my father went back to Lutsk.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He went back to Lutsk, and he was elected to the Judenrat.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we went-- we went back to Lutsk.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We went to our own unit.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We stayed there from about June, July, August-- probably two, three months.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then the-- my-- and then the ghetto was formed.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then we-- we got-- I don't know-- one hours' notice or two hours' notice that-- to take immediate-- you know, whatever we could carry and go to the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And the ghetto was in a part of Lutsk.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "There were only a few streets-- only a few streets-- only-- I don't know-- very few houses.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Normally, very few people would have lived there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They were next to a medieval castle-- Castle of Lubart-- [NON-ENGLISH], which is still standing there, of course, now.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And in those few streets and those few houses, they accommodated nearly 30,000-- 30,000 Jews.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Because some Jews, also from the villages nearby, came and stayed in the ghetto, in Lutsk.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "They had nowhere else to go.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "There wouldn't have been many of those, but there were some.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And we stayed there-- three, four families to a room, sleeping on the floor, on tables, on chairs, getting nine decas of bread-- nine decagrams, which means 90 grams of bread a day-- and practically nothing else.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I remember we had some frozen potatoes-- my sister, and my mother, and I, and my father.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And we were sharing a kitchen.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "We were-- we were sharing a room with several other families.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And eventually, my father got a little room for only our family in a house-- in a different house.",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
